{
  "_comment": "Demon Spirit Land / East Demon Spirit Sea (魔灵地 / 东海魔灵海) — a vast corrupted spirit-demon coastal region on Planet Suzaku. Canon (CANON_RI_COMPLETE_WORLD.md L57; CANON_RI_TIMELINE.md E23; CANON_RI_ECOLOGY.md Region 5): Site of Wang Lin's adoption of Thirteen as 1st disciple; Yao Xixue's first appearance (Ch. 491); All-Seer / Ling Tianhou / Blood Ancestor convergence; entrance to the Immortal Monarch's Cave Mansion (L64). The Mountain Valley Tribe (soul-refining bloodline offshoot) and Ancient Demon City sit at its heart. Yao Xixue / Blood Ancestor / Feng Mo arc takes place here. The environment is hostile: salt-blighted mist dampens divine sense, demonic-spirit energy interferes with techniques, and the coast is littered with broken restriction pillars. Spirit veins are twisted and cold. Prime Directive: the corruption and spirit-demon saturation are objective properties of this land — they exist because the region was the ancient battleground of soul-refining cultivators and demon spirits, not because anyone perceives them.",
